Bauchi State Governor Bala Mohammed has ordered the immediate payment of workers’ salaries. He gave the directive in a press statement on Friday through his Senior Special Assistant on media,Mukhtar Mohammed Gidado. The Governor directed the payment must be effected from Friday 31st May to Monday 3rd June , 2019. He, however, said workers engaged by the immediate past administration in the last one month should be exempted from the payment. ” The State Accountant General is to ensure that all persons engaged into the state service between April and May are not reflected in the payment,” he clearly stated. Mohammed charged state government workers to be committed to their work in order to ensure effective, result oriented and efficient workforce. He assured that his administration remain committed to workers’ welfare.